	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Assuming the chips are the same as those used by other clones, they are literal clones of the mask work. One advantage is that you get a better accuracy/power ratio than any software emulator today can offer. One disadvantage is that it's hideous and clunky compared to a mainstream handheld running a software emulator.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


