		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />If they are clones, they clearly have serious flaws with their cloning process, as many of the chips seem to be unable to run lots of games, and have unique bugs in other games.
<br />
<br />And so aside from power usage and perhaps a slight latency difference, the only other major thing is you get an uglier form factor with no ability to fix bugs post-production.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
